### UX Constraints вҖ” Observatory (HN-Facing)

```
CONSTRAINT                              в”Ӯ RATIONALE                    в”Ӯ PRIORITY
в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”јв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”јв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ
ZERO newsletter popups                  в”Ӯ Instant credibility kill     в”Ӯ HARD
ZERO cookie banners beyond legal min.   в”Ӯ Friction = bounce            в”Ӯ HARD
Fast load: <2s first contentful paint   в”Ӯ HN audience has zero patienceв”Ӯ HARD
Content above the fold immediately      в”Ӯ No splash pages, no hero imgsв”Ӯ HARD
All sources inline and clickable        в”Ӯ They WILL check              в”Ӯ HARD
Dark mode support                       в”Ӯ Expected by this audience    в”Ӯ HIGH
Print/PDF stylesheet that works         в”Ӯ People want to save analysis в”Ӯ HIGH
Monospace for data tables and code      в”Ӯ Visual trust signal          в”Ӯ HIGH
No social share buttons on page body    в”Ӯ Clutter tax; they share URLs в”Ӯ HIGH
Dense text OK вҖ” do NOT simplify         в”Ӯ Respects intelligence        в”Ӯ HIGH
No animations that delay content access в”Ӯ Substance over style         в”Ӯ HIGH
Methodology visible without clicking    в”Ӯ Front and center, not hidden в”Ӯ HIGH
Mobile-responsive but desktop-optimized в”Ӯ HN browses on desktop        в”Ӯ MEDIUM
Discussion link to HN thread            в”Ӯ Community expects it         в”Ӯ MEDIUM
Anchor links for every section/heading  в”Ӯ HN comments reference sectionsв”Ӯ MEDIUM
View source reveals clean, semantic HTMLв”Ӯ Audience inspects code       в”Ӯ MEDIUM
No tracking beyond minimal analytics    в”Ӯ Privacy-conscious audience   в”Ӯ MEDIUM
RSS feed for updates                    в”Ӯ HN audience uses RSS         в”Ӯ MEDIUM
```

