                                        в”Ӯ last changed                 в”Ӯ
Cross-references to related academic    в”Ӯ Situates work in literature  в”Ӯ HIGH
  literature                            в”Ӯ                              в”Ӯ
Methodology section: exhaustive,        в”Ӯ Must withstand peer scrutiny в”Ӯ HIGH
  reproducible                          в”Ӯ                              в”Ӯ
Clear statement: not peer-reviewed      в”Ӯ Honest about status          в”Ӯ HIGH
  (unless/until it becomes so)          в”Ӯ                              в”Ӯ
ORCID or equivalent for human           в”Ӯ Academic identity standard   в”Ӯ MEDIUM
  contributors                          в”Ӯ                              в”Ӯ
Semantic HTML with schema.org markup    в”Ӯ Academic search indexing     в”Ӯ MEDIUM
